{"tid":1704243,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【全港電壓大測試】每晚十點鐘，一齊開冷氣","createTime":"2019-11-10T15:21:53.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-11T02:43:30.000Z","uid":51814,"like":8,"dislike":82,"uniUserReply":26,"replies":[{"pid":"2fea0667c66406faaaac0cb6f112b216bf29e140","tid":1704243,"uid":51814,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-10T15:21:53.000Z","msg":"我諗十點鐘大嗌嘅行動已經壽終正寢咗，原因唔駛多講，大家明嘅。但係我地仍然可以做一啲嘢暗地裡集氣。<br />\n<br />\n如果要搞大罷工，首先要知道仲有幾多人仲會願意付出，又有幾多人已經做返港豬算了。仍願意付出嘅又肯做多幾多，加埋嘅力量仲有幾大影響力。<br />\n<br />\n冇人敢做民調喇，但我地不妨做些測試。每晚十點鐘，開部耗電嘅電器，睇下電力公司有冇發現電壓驟變，如果有影響，即係手足們嘅暗號話「我地仲喺度」。<br />\n<br />\n200萬真香港人，你地仲喺度嗎？"},{"pid":"24c1b5ee37f173d04efee22675c1d4f7b6479d60","tid":1704243,"uid":126621,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-10T15:22:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/jM9yEVS.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FjM9yEVS.gif&h=36baf129&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"4048373d0a3521a401c5c8158ea3b46a5144d6e0","tid":1704243,"uid":253077,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-10T15:24:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2fdfaeca42050b89a4573392601049b918b20a40","tid":1704243,"uid":62841,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-10T15:27:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"68818626b66d1223e385effbd85eb2987a4c01cb","tid":1704243,"uid":51814,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-10T15:40:04.000Z","msg":"推一推"},{"pid":"77e1004fc7e74cf0f63d69c389bbb06fff85bafe","tid":1704243,"uid":51814,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-10T16:04:22.000Z","msg":"推多推"},{"pid":"c9fb2b5a16c8fb2832e6450bcaabc9f56c355f30","tid":1704243,"uid":42043,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":1,"r